  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Labyrinth: The Wizard's Cat</strong></h2><br>Enter the dungeon and help the master wizard to find his missing cat in this oldschool dungeon crawler game with nice retro pixel art graphics.<br><br>Make your way deep into the dungeon. You will explore levels filled with challenging enemies and various traps & puzzles.<br><br>Discover powerful magical items and weapons and fight your way through hordes of enemies in this real time combat dungeon crawler.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/bb50fd55cf764f80254078d0a7566299.poster.avif?t=1724333535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/bb50fd55cf764f80254078d0a7566299.webm?t=1724333535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/bb50fd55cf764f80254078d0a7566299.mp4?t=1724333535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To help you through the dungeon you have an automap and you can save and load the game anywhere in the labyrinth.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/d949f72bc156ee25124053acde2ee0bf.poster.avif?t=1724333535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/d949f72bc156ee25124053acde2ee0bf.webm?t=1724333535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/d949f72bc156ee25124053acde2ee0bf.mp4?t=1724333535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Labyrinth: The Wizard's Cat</strong></h2><br>Enter the dungeon and help the master wizard to find his missing cat in this oldschool dungeon crawler game with nice retro pixel art graphics.<br><br>Make your way deep into the dungeon. You will explore levels filled with challenging enemies and various traps & puzzles.<br><br>Discover powerful magical items and weapons and fight your way through hordes of enemies in this real time combat dungeon crawler.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/bb50fd55cf764f80254078d0a7566299.poster.avif?t=1724333535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/bb50fd55cf764f80254078d0a7566299.webm?t=1724333535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/bb50fd55cf764f80254078d0a7566299.mp4?t=1724333535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To help you through the dungeon you have an automap and you can save and load the game anywhere in the labyrinth.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/d949f72bc156ee25124053acde2ee0bf.poster.avif?t=1724333535\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/d949f72bc156ee25124053acde2ee0bf.webm?t=1724333535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2868270/extras/d949f72bc156ee25124053acde2ee0bf.mp4?t=1724333535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
